title: List of Redditch United F.C. seasons
text:
<a href="Redditch%20United%20F.C.">Redditch United</a> is an <a href="England">English</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Redditch">Redditch</a>, <a href="Worcestershire">Worcestershire</a>. The club participates in the <a href="Southern%20League%20Premier%20Division">Southern League Premier Division</a>, and play their home games at The Valley.
